description:
EMERALD CITY OF OZ #5 (OF 5)

Publisher: MARVEL COMICS

(Writer) Eric Shanower
(Artist/Cover Artist) Skottie Young

FINAL ISSUE!

The Nome King's hordes pour into the Emerald City, bent on destroying the Land of Oz, while Dorothy, the Tin Woodman, Ozma, and the rest of their friends can only wait and watch, helpless.

The Scarecrow has one plan to save Oz, thanks to his humbug brains, and Glinda the Good has another.

Discover why this is, in fact, the last anyone will ever hear of the Land of Oz.

In Shops: 12/11/2013
$3.99
